article.description: — Josiah Jeffers had a career-high 23 points as Radford edged past South Carolina Upstate 82-77 on Thursday in a Big South Conference opener for both teams.
article.headline: Jeffers carries Radford past South Carolina Upstate 82-77
article.linkText: Jeffers carries Radford past South Carolina Upstate 82-77
article.story: SPARTANBURG, S.C. -- — Josiah Jeffers had a career-high 23 points as Radford edged past South Carolina Upstate 82-77 on Thursday in a Big South Conference opener for both teams. Lewis Djonkam and Rashun Williams each had 12 points for Radford (5-8, 1-0 Big South Conference), which snapped its four-game losing streak. Bryson Mozone had 17 points for the Spartans (3-10, 0-1). Jordan Gainey added 16 points and Dalvin White had 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
